parameters: Wow! Such an incredible number of treasures...!

Hmm, that girl over there. You seem quite fascinated by my
collection. Are you an enthusiast of sorts?

Such... such an amazing number of treasures. I couldn't help
but be mesmerized.

Ha ha ha! I am well-known as a connoisseur daimyo.
Currently, I am particularly collecting a certain item.

Yes, strange coins—commonly known as "Kika." I am gathering
old coins from all over Japan.

If you find any Kika, bring them to my mansion. I shall
exchange them for something of equal value. I'm counting on
you.

Have you brought the rare goods? Let's make a trade. (Rare
Goods ×\V[34])
元気の指輪【装飾品】　体力＋２００

Indeed, these are rare goods. Take this with
you.\c[17]--Karin has obtained the 【Ring of Vigor】!\c[0]

...Oh, it seems you don't have any rare goods on hand. Bring
them when you find them.
達人の指輪【装飾品】　技力＋１００

Indeed, these are rare goods. Take this with
you.\c[17]--Karin has obtained the 【Ring of Mastery】!\c[0]

...Oh, it seems you don't have any rare goods on hand. Bring
them when you find them.
憤怒の指輪【装飾品】　攻撃力＋８

Indeed, these are rare goods. Take this with
you.\c[17]--Karin has obtained the 【Ring of Wrath】!\c[0]

...Oh, it seems you don't have any rare goods on hand. Bring
them when you find them.
堅守の指輪【装飾品】　守備力＋１５

Indeed, these are rare goods. Take this with
you.\c[17]--Karin has obtained the 【Ring of Vigor】!\c[0]

...Oh, it seems you don't have any rare goods on hand. Bring
them when you find them.

If you find rare goods, bring them to me. We shall trade
them for something of equal value. I'm counting on you.

Ha ha ha! Thanks to you, I've gathered a lot of exotic
goods. Karin, I am grateful!

That's good to hear. It makes all the effort of collecting
them worth it.

Is there any other reward you desire? If there's something
else you want that I possess, I'm willing to give it as an
additional reward.
Well then... may I have that tiger over there?
--What? The tiger...!? You wish to have the tiger?

Yes. It's pitiful to keep it locked up in such a small cage.
There's a zoo in Ueno, and I'd like to let it roam freely
there.

...Hmm. However, this tiger is a precious part of my
collection that I've gone through great trouble to obtain
from overseas...

I understand it's a valuable collection. That's exactly why
showing it to many people would enhance your reputation as a
connoisseur daimyo... wouldn't it?

Hmm. You make a fair point... Agreed. I shall grant it to
you.

However, there's one condition: place a sign before the
tiger's exhibit--and make sure my name is prominently
included.
Yes! Understood! Then I'll take the tiger with me!

There, there. It must have been hard being in such a cramped
cage, right? I understand the pain of being inside a cell
all too well... Let's go under the wide open sky--

We almost had all the collected items go up in flames. With
the shogunate in such disarray, I'd prefer to return to my
own domain if possible...

I entrusted you with the tiger I gave you. The skill with
which you've amassed such a collection of rare goods was
splendid. I am grateful.
